title: HOUR 1- Al Leiter Oct 22, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Al Leiter Oct 22, 2020
description:
Al Leiter tells Dan where pitching is going in the major leagues. Al says using 5 or 6 different pitchers is not fun to watch. Al says the analytics decisions are being forced on managers. Al tells Dan that the Dodgers do not have 4 starting pitchers.
